Scientific:   Vulpes lagopus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Arctic tundra
Diet:         Omnivore
Lifespan:     3 years
Weight:       3.5 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         Fur changes color seasonally; survives -70 degrees Celsius

Name:         Peregrine Falcon
Scientific:   Falco peregrinus
Class:        Aves
Habitat:      Cliffs/Cities
Diet:         Carnivore
